msgstr "ໃນຟິວ \"ໝວດໝູ່\", ໃຫ້ກຳນົດໝວດໝູ່ເປັນ \"ຄ່ານາຍໜ້າ / ອັດຕາສ່ວນແບ່ງມາດຕະຖານ\", ຕົວຢ່າງ"

#. module: gallery
#: model:product.template,name:gallery.product_template_11
msgid "Once Upon a Time Before POS"
msgstr "ຄັ້ງໜຶ່ງກ່ອນມີ POS"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once satisfied, switch the <strong>\"Published\"</strong> toggle to make it "
"live."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອພໍໃຈແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ເປີດປຸ່ມ <strong>\"ເຜີຍແຜ່ແລ້ວ (Published)\"</strong> "
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມັນສະແດງຜົນຕົວຈິງ."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once the artwork is confirmed, open the <strong>Purchase App</strong>."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຜົນງານສິລະປະໄດ້ຮັບການຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບການຈັດຊື້</strong>."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the customer confirms, you can send the <strong>Sales Order</strong>—"
"congratulations on selling an artwork! For more details, check the official "
"documentation on sending and creating quotations."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງ <strong>ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ</strong>—"
"ຂໍສະແດງຄວາມຍິນດີກັບການຂາຍຜົນງານສິລະປະ! ສຳລັບລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມ, "
"ໃຫ້ກວດເບິ່ງເອກະສານທາງການກ່ຽວກັບການສົ່ງ ແລະ ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the customer expresses interest, click <strong>\"New Quotation\"</"
"strong> to generate a price proposal."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າສະແດງຄວາມສົນໃຈ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ <strong>\"ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່\"</strong> "
"ເພື່ອສ້າງຂໍ້ສະເໜີລາຄາ."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you acquire a new piece of art, adding it to your collection ensures "
"proper inventory tracking and availability online."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບຜົນງານສິລະປະໃໝ່, ການເພີ່ມມັນເຂົ້າໃນຄໍເລັກຊັນຈະຊ່ວຍຮັບປະກັນການຕິດຕາມສາງທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ ແລະ "
"ຄວາມພ້ອມໃນການຂາຍອອນລາຍ."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>CRM App</strong> and create a new opportunity for the "
"artist or supplier."
msgstr "ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບ CRM</strong> ແລະ ສ້າງໂອກາດໃໝ່ສຳລັບສິລະປິນ ຫຼື ຜູ້ສະໜອງ."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>CRM App</strong>, where you will find the new opportunity "
"in the \"New\" stage."
msgstr "ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບ CRM</strong>, ບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຈະພົບເຫັນໂອກາດໃໝ່ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນ \"ໃໝ່\"."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Inventory App</strong> and go to \"Products\" &gt; \"New\"."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)</strong> ແລະ ໄປທີ່ \"ສິນຄ້າ\" &gt; \"ໃໝ່\"."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>POS App</strong> and select \"Open Register\" to begin "
